{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Structure","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSSwitchItemV","title":"OUDSSwitchItem","platforms":[{"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false,"name":"iOS"},{"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"name":"macOS"},{"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"16.0","deprecated":false,"name":"tvOS"},{"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"name":"visionOS"},{"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"11.0","deprecated":false,"name":"watchOS"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSwitchItem"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSwitchItem"}],"role":"symbol"},"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Switch item is a UI element that allows to toggle between two states, typically “On” and “Off”, and used to enable or disable features, options or settings."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Switch Item covers a wider range of contexts by allowing to toggle the visibility of additional text labels and icon assets."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSwitchItem"}]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Layouts","anchor":"Layouts","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"inverse","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing switch indicator and a leading optional decorative icon"}]}]}]},{"text":"Indicator states","anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The switch indicator has two available states set as a boolean property that determines whether the toggle is on or off."}]},{"text":"Particular cases","anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as disabled."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The switch can be also outlined in some cases."}]},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and optional texts and a custom switch trait."}]},{"text":"Forbidden by design","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ Localizable from bundle can also be used","    OUDSSwitchItem(LocalizedStringKey(\"notifications_setting\"), bundle: Bundle.module, isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, and a description text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, description: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading switch with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, description: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an additional label, a description text and an icon.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   description: \"The Beatles\",","                   isReversed: true,","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, a description text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   description: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                   isReversed: true,","                   isError: true,","                   hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   isError: true,","                   errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                   hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\", isOn: $isOn)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related switch as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you need to flip your icon depending to the layout direction or not (e.g. if RTL mode lose semantics  \/ meanings):"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, flipLeadingIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-switch","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]},{"text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading","level":2},{"text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchItem_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"text":"Orange Compact","anchor":"Orange-Compact","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchItem_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}]},{"text":"Sosh","anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchItem_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"text":"Wireframe","anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchItem_Wireframe","type":"image"}]},{"name":"Version","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"1.5.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","type":"aside"},{"name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.14.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","type":"aside"}]}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/init(_:isOn:description:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/init(_:tableName:bundle:isOn:description:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:)"],"title":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/body"],"title":"Instance Properties"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/View-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSwitchItem/body":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem\/body","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/body","title":"body","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"body","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"ic_folder_categories.png":{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/ic_folder_categories.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"ty